gpt_response:
67 atoms

C11H23NOS represents a chemical formula for a molecule. To determine the total number of atoms in this molecule, we sum the number of each type of atom present: 

Carbon (C) has 11 atoms
Hydrogen (H) has 23 atoms
Nitrogen (N) has 1 atom
Oxygen (O) has 1 atom
Sulfur (S) has 1 atom

Adding these up, we get a total of 11 + 23 + 1 + 1 + 1 = 67 atoms in C11H23NOS.
